imdb.plot outline: "Temporal Financial Travellings" is a better title. Gary J.J. Powell and H.G. Wells author screenplay, and one teleplays. A Futuristic Union Man, code named Courage, brings the Guilds, the Unions of the Future, into a present past of reality. Creation Studios, once officially legitimized with all its angles and growth, can take on this Project. The Financier, Gary finds his past lifetimes full of Old money and lifetimes such as JJ Astor, A.M. Rothschild, and Otto of Hapsburg that solidifies his new money as a Guilder. Exotic locations and under various ospice The Financier makes hand over fist rewards and benefits for all involved, including the audiences.
